-- Exxaro Says Planned Reorganization of Business May Lead to 300 Job Losses
-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 2010-11-02T14:44:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-02/exxaro-says-planned-reorganization-of-business-may-lead-to-300-job-losses.html
Exxaro Resources Ltd. said a planned
reorganization of some of its operations to improve productivity
and reduce costs may lead to as many as 300 job losses.  The company will start talks with employees and labor
unions this month, Exxaro said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  